snippet: Jurors have so far been unable to agree on the charges against Officer Gilberto Valle, who is accused of plotting to kidnap, kill and cannibalize women.
abstract: Jurors enter second day of deliberations, without reaching a verdict, in case against Gilberto Valle, New York City police officer accused of plotting to kidnap, kill and cannibalize women.
lead_paragraph: Jurors have so far been unable to agree on the charges against Officer Gilberto Valle, who is accused of plotting to kidnap, kill and cannibalize women.

headline.seo: In Cannibal Case, Jury Deliberates for 2nd Day Without Verdict
headline.main: Jury Still at Work in Cannibal Case
headline.print_headline: Jury Still at Work In Cannibal Case
